snippet.title: Saturday Morning RPG Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Get your time travel gear ready, we're taking you on a trip back to the 80's! Here's a sneak peek at our upcoming game "Saturday Morning RPG" that has been born from a year's worth of labor and love. Our hero, Marty, will be taking you on an adventure visiting old friends from the golden Saturday morning cartoon era in an original story brought to you by Mighty Rabbit Studios.
